{
  "text": "Principal components analysis (PCA) of the protein NSAF scores was performed using COVAIN [CITATION_1] . A PCA of the pollen proteins revealed that the samples could be separated into two major groups ( Figure 4A) , with one including only the HS-exposed microspores (P-HS), and the other including DPGs derived from the following three treatment Ethephon pre-treated-Control P-E-C 941",
